                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:新細明體">◎<span style="font-family:times new roman; font-size:7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://sktdeity.pixnet.net/album/photo/198105662"><img alt="server-xml - context path_1" border="0" src="http://pic.pimg.tw/sktdeity/1340870987-2656772539.jpg" title="server-xml - context path_1" /></a> &nbsp; </span></span></p>

                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:新細明體">◎<span style="font-family:times new roman; font-size:7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://sktdeity.pixnet.net/album/photo/198105664"><img alt="server-xml - context path_2" border="0" src="http://pic.pimg.tw/sktdeity/1340870988-3866233055.jpg" title="server-xml - context path_2" /></a> &nbsp; </span></span></p>

                                                        <p><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="color:blue">&lt;Context</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color:red"> path</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color:blue">=&rdquo;/struts&rdquo; </span><span lang="EN-US" style="color:red">docBase</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color:blue">=&rdquo;D:\MyEclipse 10 Workstation\struts2\WebRoot&rdquo; </span><span lang="EN-US" style="color:red">workDir</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color:blue">=&rdquo; D:\MyEclipse 10 Workstation\struts2\WebRoot&rdquo;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color:red"> reloadable</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color:blue">=&rdquo;true&rdquo;/&gt;</span></strong></p>

                                                        <p><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="color:blue">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>

                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:新細明體">◎<span style="font-family:times new roman; font-size:7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:新細明體">這裡的</span><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="color:red">docBase</span></strong> <span style="font-family:新細明體">及</span> <strong><span lang="EN-US" style="color:red">workDir </span></strong><span style="font-family:新細明體">設定為自己</span>struts2<span style="font-family:新細明體">的工作路徑</span> , <span style="font-family:新細明體">請特別注意</span> , path <span style="font-family:新細明體">這裡指向</span><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="color:red">localhost:8080/struts2/ </span></strong><span style="font-family:新細明體">，</span><span style="font-family:新細明體">打好了之後</span> <span style="font-family:新細明體">存檔關閉即可</span> <span style="font-family:新細明體">。</span></p>

                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:新細明體">◎<span style="font-family:times new roman; font-size:7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:新細明體">接下來開始設定</span> Tomcat 7 for Eclipse</p>

                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:新細明體">◎<span style="font-family:times new roman; font-size:7pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:新細明體">切換回</span>Myeclipse 10 , <span style="font-family:新細明體">點選工具列上</span> Windows -&gt; Preferences -&gt; <span style="font-family:新細明體">先找到</span> Java -&gt; Install JREs , <span style="font-family:新細明體">看是否設定好</span>java path , <span style="font-family:新細明體">若沒有的話</span> <span style="font-family:新細明體">點擊</span> Add -&gt; Standard JVM -&gt; JRE home <span style="font-family:新細明體">選擇</span> JDK home , <span style="font-family:新細明體">我這指向</span>C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_03 , <span style="font-family:新細明體">點擊</span>finish <span style="font-family:新細明體">完成</span> JDK <span style="font-family:新細明體">設定</span> . <span style="font-family:新細明體">接者找到</span> Windows -&gt; Preferences -&gt; MyEclipse -&gt; Servers -&gt; Tomcat 7.x (<span style="font-family:新細明體">注意</span> , <span style="font-family:新細明體">我這裡使用</span>7.0 <span style="font-family:新細明體">故選</span> 7) ,&nbsp; <span style="font-family:新細明體">點擊</span>Tomcat 7.x <span style="font-family:新細明體">會看到</span> Tomcat 7.x server <span style="font-family:新細明體">預設為</span> Disable , <span style="font-family:新細明體">將他選為</span>Enable <span style="font-family:新細明體">啟用</span> , Tomcat home directory <span style="font-family:新細明體">選擇</span> c:\xampp\tomcat <span style="font-family:新細明體">確定</span> , <span style="font-family:新細明體">展開</span>Tomcat 7.x , <span style="font-family:新細明體">移動至</span>JDK ,Tomcat 7.x JDK name <span style="font-family:新細明體">選擇</span> jdk1.7.0_03 , <span style="font-family:新細明體">若沒有的話請自行新增</span> .<span style="font-family:新細明體">隨後看到</span>Lauch -&gt; <span style="font-family:新細明體">將</span> Default Tomcat 7.x lauch mode -&gt; Debug mode <span style="font-family:新細明體">改為</span> Run mode <span style="font-family:新細明體">之後點擊右下角</span> Apply <span style="font-family:新細明體">之後點擊</span> OK , Tomcat <span style="font-family:新細明體">就設定完成</span> <span style="font-family:新細明體">。</span></p>

